{"id": "nat_0", "text": "The birch canoe slid on the smooth planks.", "audio_duration_s": 2.3219954648526078, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 2.992874947553929, "dnsmos_sig": 3.4615830206938774, "dnsmos_bak": 3.660679899945724}
{"id": "nat_1", "text": "Glue the sheet to the dark blue background.", "audio_duration_s": 2.2291156462585033, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.0906840889673055, "dnsmos_sig": 3.3593108892058043, "dnsmos_bak": 4.026928118718883}
{"id": "nat_2", "text": "It is easy to tell the depth of a well.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9504761904761905, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.3285927824219628, "dnsmos_sig": 3.592359403400955, "dnsmos_bak": 4.113193761819376}
{"id": "nat_3", "text": "These days a chicken leg is a rare dish.", "audio_duration_s": 2.507755102040816, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.3377906052726143, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5704886705993637, "dnsmos_bak": 4.0729033991310235}
{"id": "nat_4", "text": "Rice is often served in round bowls.", "audio_duration_s": 2.136235827664399, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2335010532934234, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5618611671105134, "dnsmos_bak": 3.938291850061438}
{"id": "nat_5", "text": "The juice of lemons makes fine punch.", "audio_duration_s": 2.3219954648526078, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 2.976857089386341, "dnsmos_sig": 3.2541613536076324, "dnsmos_bak": 3.903560781895247}
{"id": "nat_6", "text": "The box was thrown beside the parked truck.", "audio_duration_s": 2.36843537414966, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2418929604732245, "dnsmos_sig": 3.4864332863554957, "dnsmos_bak": 4.1126513834040415}
{"id": "nat_7", "text": "The hogs were fed chopped corn and garbage.", "audio_duration_s": 2.414875283446712, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.0799674315747616, "dnsmos_sig": 3.381452099504204, "dnsmos_bak": 3.9439100515914562}
{"id": "nat_8", "text": "Four hours of steady work faced us.", "audio_duration_s": 2.2755555555555556, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.388887088353799, "dnsmos_sig": 3.622910829434784, "dnsmos_bak": 4.135492970922359}
{"id": "nat_9", "text": "Large size in stockings is hard to sell.", "audio_duration_s": 2.36843537414966, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.408811932300842, "dnsmos_sig": 3.645951181898043, "dnsmos_bak": 4.136722210344601}
{"id": "nat_10", "text": "The boy was there when the sun rose.", "audio_duration_s": 1.811156462585034, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.1897789634742475, "dnsmos_sig": 3.509029735449552, "dnsmos_bak": 3.9102981208135845}
{"id": "nat_11", "text": "A rod is used to catch pink salmon.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9969160997732427, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.199031724867608, "dnsmos_sig": 3.511986707280307, "dnsmos_bak": 4.004119858904136}
{"id": "nat_12", "text": "The source of the huge river is the clear spring.", "audio_duration_s": 2.507755102040816, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.294749127048848, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5504206543221595, "dnsmos_bak": 4.113038001224481}
{"id": "nat_13", "text": "Kick the ball straight and follow through.", "audio_duration_s": 3.250793650793651, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.1748759113758602, "dnsmos_sig": 3.3979889974244477, "dnsmos_bak": 4.138718019921933}
{"id": "nat_14", "text": "Help the woman get back to her feet.", "audio_duration_s": 1.811156462585034, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.3460493565683516, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5663680231803783, "dnsmos_bak": 4.176738818388349}
{"id": "nat_15", "text": "A blue crane is a tall wading bird.", "audio_duration_s": 2.3219954648526078, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.258428738150365, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5234520545410706, "dnsmos_bak": 4.1169723476899405}
{"id": "nat_16", "text": "It is hard to erase blue or red ink.", "audio_duration_s": 2.507755102040816, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 2.7459504605024123, "dnsmos_sig": 3.20133500854463, "dnsmos_bak": 3.5653864557839707}
{"id": "nat_17", "text": "Write quickly and meet me at the dock.", "audio_duration_s": 1.7647165532879818, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.17947571648834, "dnsmos_sig": 3.4529150774460424, "dnsmos_bak": 4.0335555874297535}
{"id": "nat_18", "text": "The two talked quietly in the dim light.", "audio_duration_s": 2.2291156462585033, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.1933276974104956, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5014133446185958, "dnsmos_bak": 4.001214997966275}
{"id": "nat_19", "text": "The hail pattered on the burnt red tiles.", "audio_duration_s": 2.647074829931973, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.1553743924966082, "dnsmos_sig": 3.4549782027616405, "dnsmos_bak": 3.931822033325907}
{"id": "nat_20", "text": "The sand drifted down the steep slope.", "audio_duration_s": 2.3219954648526078, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2360924284656862, "dnsmos_sig": 3.497529516991356, "dnsmos_bak": 4.08302648371103}
{"id": "nat_21", "text": "Oak is strong and also gives shade.", "audio_duration_s": 2.2755555555555556, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.360161259644862, "dnsmos_sig": 3.619397837690451, "dnsmos_bak": 4.104245858790612}
{"id": "nat_22", "text": "Cats and dogs each hate the other.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9040362811791383, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.091962156614249, "dnsmos_sig": 3.396544160398959, "dnsmos_bak": 4.019101005482294}
{"id": "nat_23", "text": "The pipe began to rust while new.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9040362811791383, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.258911747995919, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5113161503931085, "dnsmos_bak": 4.128242165356347}
{"id": "nat_24", "text": "Open the crate but don't break the glass.", "audio_duration_s": 2.647074829931973, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2837162990380886, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5327396753763693, "dnsmos_bak": 4.116082094855223}
{"id": "nat_25", "text": "Add the sum to the product of these three.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9504761904761905, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2626402965656482, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5566670017566575, "dnsmos_bak": 4.040758545491156}
{"id": "nat_26", "text": "Thieves who rob friends deserve jail.", "audio_duration_s": 2.043356009070295, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2386166891285373, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5139806811341012, "dnsmos_bak": 4.030623961626034}
{"id": "nat_27", "text": "The ripe taste of cheese improves with age.", "audio_duration_s": 2.507755102040816, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.3636862895131396, "dnsmos_sig": 3.625081333676849, "dnsmos_bak": 4.139063247980504}
{"id": "nat_28", "text": "Act on these orders with great speed.", "audio_duration_s": 2.089795918367347, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.236105394225391, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5561201014861297, "dnsmos_bak": 4.007453269012256}
{"id": "nat_29", "text": "The hush of night came on the water.", "audio_duration_s": 1.7182766439909296, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.40483235584904, "dnsmos_sig": 3.643492030236284, "dnsmos_bak": 4.132878075007846}
{"id": "nat_30", "text": "Flax makes linen for many a dress.", "audio_duration_s": 2.089795918367347, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 2.9699551158711515, "dnsmos_sig": 3.3608134198651696, "dnsmos_bak": 3.676499781343299}
{"id": "nat_31", "text": "Hoist the load to your left shoulder.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9969160997732427, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.1225282515707313, "dnsmos_sig": 3.484563674277816, "dnsmos_bak": 3.8967403279810084}
{"id": "nat_32", "text": "Take the winding path to reach the lake.", "audio_duration_s": 2.089795918367347, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.3231408328530443, "dnsmos_sig": 3.55936409626645, "dnsmos_bak": 4.154904089908889}
{"id": "nat_33", "text": "Note closely the size of the gas tank.", "audio_duration_s": 2.089795918367347, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.325218853004607, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5782288831809366, "dnsmos_bak": 4.141471587245477}
{"id": "nat_34", "text": "Wipe the grease off his dirty face.", "audio_duration_s": 2.2291156462585033, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.199662969207935, "dnsmos_sig": 3.4192789622925828, "dnsmos_bak": 4.153076475957888}
{"id": "nat_35", "text": "Mend the coat before wearing it again.", "audio_duration_s": 2.182675736961451, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.3473911289333924, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5785071741586036, "dnsmos_bak": 4.158462721334456}
{"id": "nat_36", "text": "The lease ran out in sixteen weeks.", "audio_duration_s": 2.2291156462585033, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.334787789666513, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5696703400782765, "dnsmos_bak": 4.167191349504368}
{"id": "nat_37", "text": "Both parts of the design came together.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9969160997732427, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2587410771107237, "dnsmos_sig": 3.470411330196674, "dnsmos_bak": 4.164040895411229}
{"id": "nat_38", "text": "Sewing hems and darns takes skill.", "audio_duration_s": 2.36843537414966, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.244900431043233, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5018263931730917, "dnsmos_bak": 4.063593996722621}
{"id": "nat_39", "text": "The architect planned a new city hall.", "audio_duration_s": 2.136235827664399, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.0654369949325577, "dnsmos_sig": 3.356013218513567, "dnsmos_bak": 3.9371100422671277}
{"id": "nat_40", "text": "The small red lamp stood in a corner.", "audio_duration_s": 2.2291156462585033, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.298104879250403, "dnsmos_sig": 3.594769315017925, "dnsmos_bak": 4.023658207831718}
{"id": "nat_41", "text": "The large box came by truck to town.", "audio_duration_s": 2.182675736961451, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.3785638477152333, "dnsmos_sig": 3.6184162117020797, "dnsmos_bak": 4.15239233185049}
{"id": "nat_42", "text": "The men fought hard to save the fort.", "audio_duration_s": 1.811156462585034, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2738806354324703, "dnsmos_sig": 3.500331192796692, "dnsmos_bak": 4.133785935371774}
{"id": "nat_43", "text": "The horse chewed his bit and nodded.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9040362811791383, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.024351631514047, "dnsmos_sig": 3.3293502533635118, "dnsmos_bak": 3.9280295408097565}
{"id": "nat_44", "text": "Three of the men were hurt badly.", "audio_duration_s": 1.6253968253968254, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.297672578392894, "dnsmos_sig": 3.530270841034167, "dnsmos_bak": 4.103233314868913}
{"id": "nat_45", "text": "Ripe pears are fit for a queen's table.", "audio_duration_s": 2.36843537414966, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.268655140634202, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5223892033257456, "dnsmos_bak": 4.169724961702859}
{"id": "nat_46", "text": "The dark room was lit by a red light.", "audio_duration_s": 2.089795918367347, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.0999540433487724, "dnsmos_sig": 3.4023065597343374, "dnsmos_bak": 4.005142270291728}
{"id": "nat_47", "text": "The fox hid in the tall grass nearby.", "audio_duration_s": 2.2291156462585033, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.32928690383739, "dnsmos_sig": 3.581768011859831, "dnsmos_bak": 4.1115251139676765}
{"id": "nat_48", "text": "We saw eight tiny goats on the hillside.", "audio_duration_s": 2.2755555555555556, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.283283395437041, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5383940132511666, "dnsmos_bak": 4.074766854877853}
{"id": "nat_49", "text": "The cats purred softly on the warm rug.", "audio_duration_s": 2.2755555555555556, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2267209367849183, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5670169919684125, "dnsmos_bak": 3.9189556792402955}
{"id": "nat_50", "text": "The silver bell rang at dawn.", "audio_duration_s": 1.5789569160997732, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.3247815124058064, "dnsmos_sig": 3.6052242967910537, "dnsmos_bak": 4.087145521812556}
{"id": "nat_51", "text": "The crowd cheered the band with pride.", "audio_duration_s": 2.2291156462585033, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.278058436887342, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5648362296306066, "dnsmos_bak": 4.062998351153675}
{"id": "nat_52", "text": "She baked fresh bread every morning.", "audio_duration_s": 2.136235827664399, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 2.9950248099656345, "dnsmos_sig": 3.3390231656841722, "dnsmos_bak": 3.8414282208958483}
{"id": "nat_53", "text": "The train reached the bridge at noon.", "audio_duration_s": 1.8575963718820863, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.1775875104805444, "dnsmos_sig": 3.4394595672422086, "dnsmos_bak": 4.0299196122101435}
{"id": "nat_54", "text": "Cool winds blew from the distant peaks.", "audio_duration_s": 2.2291156462585033, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.5060578465146484, "dnsmos_sig": 3.720509973586648, "dnsmos_bak": 4.179744372727475}
{"id": "nat_55", "text": "The old dog slept by the warm fire.", "audio_duration_s": 2.36843537414966, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.212180148901508, "dnsmos_sig": 3.4900424914898736, "dnsmos_bak": 4.070418315065715}
{"id": "nat_56", "text": "Bright stars filled the clear night sky.", "audio_duration_s": 2.414875283446712, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.291817779022591, "dnsmos_sig": 3.552011150656787, "dnsmos_bak": 4.0632288182510905}
{"id": "nat_57", "text": "The child built a castle in the sand.", "audio_duration_s": 2.182675736961451, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.081465737821361, "dnsmos_sig": 3.459762982815403, "dnsmos_bak": 3.8790445897698604}
{"id": "nat_58", "text": "Rain soaked the dry and barren plain.", "audio_duration_s": 2.2755555555555556, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.325868791399422, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5824021152608214, "dnsmos_bak": 4.095022264679524}
{"id": "nat_59", "text": "The boat moved quietly past the shore.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9969160997732427, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2647856211473, "dnsmos_sig": 3.519574516447299, "dnsmos_bak": 4.110741851611024}
{"id": "nat_60", "text": "Plums ripen in the warm summer sun.", "audio_duration_s": 2.043356009070295, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.083443889701498, "dnsmos_sig": 3.381989952168013, "dnsmos_bak": 4.013971541506527}
{"id": "nat_61", "text": "The lock was jammed but opened at last.", "audio_duration_s": 2.2291156462585033, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.302679008024369, "dnsmos_sig": 3.549798235571869, "dnsmos_bak": 4.127236663551541}
{"id": "nat_62", "text": "The key to the cabinet was misplaced.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9969160997732427, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.065486613835788, "dnsmos_sig": 3.418280272392168, "dnsmos_bak": 3.8304640619361403}
{"id": "nat_63", "text": "The cup shattered on the stone floor.", "audio_duration_s": 1.811156462585034, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.131627705510149, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5498844506921943, "dnsmos_bak": 3.855325975542337}
{"id": "nat_64", "text": "A black bear crossed the narrow trail.", "audio_duration_s": 2.136235827664399, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.300981684035741, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5347563774817368, "dnsmos_bak": 4.1489553104909325}
{"id": "nat_65", "text": "Fresh dew glistened on the green leaves.", "audio_duration_s": 2.3219954648526078, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.255419914807153, "dnsmos_sig": 3.527807671061046, "dnsmos_bak": 4.0414518667828245}
{"id": "nat_66", "text": "The lamp cast a soft glow on the table.", "audio_duration_s": 2.36843537414966, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.402522557817403, "dnsmos_sig": 3.622295234103656, "dnsmos_bak": 4.138785172982448}
{"id": "nat_67", "text": "Strong winds bent the tall pine trees.", "audio_duration_s": 2.7399546485260773, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.3828800626889097, "dnsmos_sig": 3.6066162493539404, "dnsmos_bak": 4.129440847834861}
{"id": "nat_68", "text": "A robin sang from the old oak branch.", "audio_duration_s": 2.2291156462585033, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.3384502815287402, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5607720051924283, "dnsmos_bak": 4.14906884400503}
{"id": "nat_69", "text": "The crowd fell silent when he spoke.", "audio_duration_s": 1.8575963718820863, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2338979540528427, "dnsmos_sig": 3.535462276925118, "dnsmos_bak": 4.086434196395045}
{"id": "nat_70", "text": "Green fields stretched to the far horizon.", "audio_duration_s": 2.647074829931973, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2884469813709414, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5803545735984312, "dnsmos_bak": 4.048181771518767}
{"id": "nat_71", "text": "The river ran swift and cold today.", "audio_duration_s": 2.3219954648526078, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.142031318405126, "dnsmos_sig": 3.468497092972016, "dnsmos_bak": 3.9916485592264372}
{"id": "nat_72", "text": "The flag waved high in the morning breeze.", "audio_duration_s": 2.507755102040816, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.3204427142624704, "dnsmos_sig": 3.560485923589991, "dnsmos_bak": 4.105180497579669}
{"id": "nat_73", "text": "Blue jays flew low over the meadow.", "audio_duration_s": 1.811156462585034, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.026621637184318, "dnsmos_sig": 3.530632161475867, "dnsmos_bak": 3.6782911557815026}
{"id": "nat_74", "text": "The forge was lit at break of day.", "audio_duration_s": 2.043356009070295, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 2.9608513944437935, "dnsmos_sig": 3.2517563467329333, "dnsmos_bak": 3.968619187772685}
{"id": "nat_75", "text": "The sparrows hopped on the garden wall.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9040362811791383, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.114047736748283, "dnsmos_sig": 3.3776217346476436, "dnsmos_bak": 4.055912134018855}
{"id": "nat_76", "text": "Fill the car before you drive into town.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9969160997732427, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.22421815856416, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5274404687462835, "dnsmos_bak": 4.032899616618995}
{"id": "nat_77", "text": "A cud of grass hung from the heifer's lip.", "audio_duration_s": 2.414875283446712, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.087625323940402, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5537940732767277, "dnsmos_bak": 3.707021213569236}
{"id": "nat_78", "text": "The seed grew into a giant oak tree.", "audio_duration_s": 2.507755102040816, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2270524887579457, "dnsmos_sig": 3.4583715263251844, "dnsmos_bak": 4.094890669585862}
{"id": "nat_79", "text": "A worm ate through the wooden plank.", "audio_duration_s": 2.089795918367347, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.360640904494641, "dnsmos_sig": 3.618396191923165, "dnsmos_bak": 4.134896606799993}
{"id": "nat_80", "text": "The team scored in the last few seconds.", "audio_duration_s": 2.3219954648526078, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.319207414793079, "dnsmos_sig": 3.566325398524801, "dnsmos_bak": 4.068250089678998}
{"id": "nat_81", "text": "The glass jar held the bright red jam.", "audio_duration_s": 2.2755555555555556, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.326524454675608, "dnsmos_sig": 3.584785875089427, "dnsmos_bak": 4.128572900230404}
{"id": "nat_82", "text": "The leaves fell slowly in the autumn air.", "audio_duration_s": 2.507755102040816, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 2.644752928265711, "dnsmos_sig": 3.4152786180041668, "dnsmos_bak": 3.098899279415457}
{"id": "nat_83", "text": "The farmer planted seeds in long rows.", "audio_duration_s": 2.36843537414966, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.4446114967030823, "dnsmos_sig": 3.6686759466786305, "dnsmos_bak": 4.156310006681779}
{"id": "nat_84", "text": "The clock struck twelve at midnight.", "audio_duration_s": 1.7647165532879818, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 2.9847215427908553, "dnsmos_sig": 3.2937391000565484, "dnsmos_bak": 3.9105661262498885}
{"id": "nat_85", "text": "A pale moon rose over the distant hills.", "audio_duration_s": 2.647074829931973, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.370872775988002, "dnsmos_sig": 3.591381717811092, "dnsmos_bak": 4.130891840013759}
{"id": "nat_86", "text": "The stream carved a path through the stone.", "audio_duration_s": 2.2755555555555556, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.1883044602607833, "dnsmos_sig": 3.475709696452925, "dnsmos_bak": 4.041728441671792}
{"id": "nat_87", "text": "Bright flowers bloomed along the fence.", "audio_duration_s": 2.089795918367347, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2290601118315436, "dnsmos_sig": 3.4922402323760204, "dnsmos_bak": 4.07768724730638}
{"id": "nat_88", "text": "The snow lay deep on the mountain pass.", "audio_duration_s": 2.461315192743764, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.4611216023928826, "dnsmos_sig": 3.694118684557794, "dnsmos_bak": 4.159025747489976}
{"id": "nat_89", "text": "The eagle soared above the canyon rim.", "audio_duration_s": 2.2291156462585033, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.275603059577434, "dnsmos_sig": 3.594708830864325, "dnsmos_bak": 3.999758708193731}
{"id": "nat_90", "text": "The gate swung open with a loud creak.", "audio_duration_s": 2.182675736961451, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.301150839348872, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5434398296038867, "dnsmos_bak": 4.1248609977969135}
{"id": "nat_91", "text": "The wolf howled at the cold winter moon.", "audio_duration_s": 2.5541950113378684, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.0917034727792063, "dnsmos_sig": 3.458465149848797, "dnsmos_bak": 3.830785208465673}
{"id": "nat_92", "text": "A candle flickered in the draft of wind.", "audio_duration_s": 2.2755555555555556, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.3547832446054158, "dnsmos_sig": 3.653110417629045, "dnsmos_bak": 4.095359623929334}
{"id": "nat_93", "text": "The road curved sharply past the barn.", "audio_duration_s": 2.36843537414966, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.317065215739337, "dnsmos_sig": 3.573644354380995, "dnsmos_bak": 4.123986932823603}
{"id": "nat_94", "text": "Wool is spun into yarn for warm cloth.", "audio_duration_s": 2.6006349206349206, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2160630751140373, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5360408827655085, "dnsmos_bak": 3.918139267724893}
{"id": "nat_95", "text": "The crowd surged through the narrow gate.", "audio_duration_s": 2.136235827664399, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.3428653435336533, "dnsmos_sig": 3.6011280470942255, "dnsmos_bak": 4.093080381405925}
{"id": "nat_96", "text": "The owl hunted mice in the dark field.", "audio_duration_s": 2.136235827664399, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.3295044442279136, "dnsmos_sig": 3.599315687635676, "dnsmos_bak": 4.05315343396948}
{"id": "nat_97", "text": "The pond froze solid in January.", "audio_duration_s": 2.2291156462585033, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2465267405523988, "dnsmos_sig": 3.59245905199325, "dnsmos_bak": 3.978357981391049}
{"id": "nat_98", "text": "A flock of geese flew in a V-shape.", "audio_duration_s": 2.089795918367347, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 2.9898337647658892, "dnsmos_sig": 3.360420210987882, "dnsmos_bak": 3.8013544336285756}
{"id": "nat_99", "text": "The tide ebbed low on the rocky coast.", "audio_duration_s": 2.3219954648526078, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.335307875285796, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5653553113068264, "dnsmos_bak": 4.1097592104730145}
{"id": "nat_100", "text": "The flame burned bright in the dark cave.", "audio_duration_s": 2.5541950113378684, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.1711764447756217, "dnsmos_sig": 3.450774744915789, "dnsmos_bak": 4.016231805230015}
{"id": "nat_101", "text": "The mill ground grain into fine flour.", "audio_duration_s": 2.182675736961451, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.317619407135954, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5972645898444644, "dnsmos_bak": 4.094451371505669}
{"id": "nat_102", "text": "The stag grazed near the edge of the wood.", "audio_duration_s": 2.36843537414966, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.230284487603666, "dnsmos_sig": 3.4423501695114957, "dnsmos_bak": 4.122046051553133}
{"id": "nat_103", "text": "The well dried up in the hot summer.", "audio_duration_s": 1.7647165532879818, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.254058360350588, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5128352762936665, "dnsmos_bak": 4.093712506648202}
{"id": "nat_104", "text": "The swift brown fox ran past the log.", "audio_duration_s": 2.6006349206349206, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.1825448446459057, "dnsmos_sig": 3.4657445042377955, "dnsmos_bak": 4.051747793976145}
{"id": "nat_105", "text": "A stone wall bordered the old estate.", "audio_duration_s": 2.36843537414966, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.216362090342186, "dnsmos_sig": 3.480223634368476, "dnsmos_bak": 4.09413682247751}
{"id": "nat_106", "text": "The bell rang twice before it stopped.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9504761904761905, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.1736785102041796, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5293894552350356, "dnsmos_bak": 3.9526529990048194}
{"id": "nat_107", "text": "The hawk soared high on the warm updraft.", "audio_duration_s": 2.7399546485260773, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.124345263828629, "dnsmos_sig": 3.4293413655709113, "dnsmos_bak": 3.8916442214184555}
{"id": "nat_108", "text": "The sharp knife cut the rough cord.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9040362811791383, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.089958698950671, "dnsmos_sig": 3.382923460236897, "dnsmos_bak": 3.9435360859321036}
{"id": "nat_109", "text": "The colt pranced in the wide green field.", "audio_duration_s": 2.36843537414966, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.278194478618562, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5568916836794244, "dnsmos_bak": 4.07225288893463}
{"id": "nat_110", "text": "A fish leaped from the calm blue lake.", "audio_duration_s": 2.461315192743764, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.285448814241201, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5276892554388346, "dnsmos_bak": 4.1123470415009065}
{"id": "nat_111", "text": "The damp ground smelled of fresh rain.", "audio_duration_s": 2.136235827664399, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2846354061057674, "dnsmos_sig": 3.610712726314629, "dnsmos_bak": 3.9999765019631797}
{"id": "nat_112", "text": "The cart was loaded with heavy stone.", "audio_duration_s": 2.089795918367347, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2071612129951945, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5375693248317086, "dnsmos_bak": 4.001462150926681}
{"id": "nat_113", "text": "The long white rope coiled on the deck.", "audio_duration_s": 2.043356009070295, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.077795746142896, "dnsmos_sig": 3.509792813447208, "dnsmos_bak": 3.7696827209498704}
{"id": "nat_114", "text": "The pine tree grew tall and straight.", "audio_duration_s": 2.089795918367347, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.3315872236039645, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5874587896636467, "dnsmos_bak": 4.112046589243635}
{"id": "nat_115", "text": "The coal burned slowly in the iron stove.", "audio_duration_s": 2.7399546485260773, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.3054787833911843, "dnsmos_sig": 3.594117296141652, "dnsmos_bak": 4.057241542303959}
{"id": "nat_116", "text": "A gust of wind tore the sail apart.", "audio_duration_s": 2.2291156462585033, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.3589741264257755, "dnsmos_sig": 3.617206385515601, "dnsmos_bak": 4.132783682243374}
{"id": "nat_117", "text": "The goat climbed steep rocky paths easily.", "audio_duration_s": 2.693514739229025, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.198159669586027, "dnsmos_sig": 3.512280208786541, "dnsmos_bak": 3.9116626989514467}
{"id": "nat_118", "text": "The red sun sank below the flat plain.", "audio_duration_s": 2.414875283446712, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.308965434409418, "dnsmos_sig": 3.549976335171749, "dnsmos_bak": 4.14956490502506}
{"id": "nat_119", "text": "The wheat field swayed in the warm breeze.", "audio_duration_s": 2.414875283446712, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 2.7080900704201487, "dnsmos_sig": 3.400245908706325, "dnsmos_bak": 3.2139019879113886}
{"id": "nat_120", "text": "The thick fog rolled in from the sea.", "audio_duration_s": 2.2291156462585033, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.1746190869473274, "dnsmos_sig": 3.4999740356631968, "dnsmos_bak": 3.969294803556577}
{"id": "nat_121", "text": "The drum beat loud and steady all night.", "audio_duration_s": 2.043356009070295, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.0948594366748265, "dnsmos_sig": 3.3825494782993117, "dnsmos_bak": 4.0143476640502245}
{"id": "nat_122", "text": "The fox left tracks in the new snow.", "audio_duration_s": 2.136235827664399, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2907640160374996, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5482557865528674, "dnsmos_bak": 4.109624676050418}
{"id": "nat_123", "text": "The light faded as the sun went down.", "audio_duration_s": 2.089795918367347, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.0346854718941403, "dnsmos_sig": 3.446578118656564, "dnsmos_bak": 3.8073160690227654}
{"id": "nat_124", "text": "A small boat drifted on the still lake.", "audio_duration_s": 2.136235827664399, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.076186652097941, "dnsmos_sig": 3.357953601302563, "dnsmos_bak": 4.000320020225408}
{"id": "nat_125", "text": "The cook prepared a fresh pot of soup.", "audio_duration_s": 2.182675736961451, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.0676928416570663, "dnsmos_sig": 3.3645487355085644, "dnsmos_bak": 3.9293154389151317}
{"id": "nat_126", "text": "The old mill wheel turned in the stream.", "audio_duration_s": 2.089795918367347, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.0936822765361662, "dnsmos_sig": 3.49993639343932, "dnsmos_bak": 3.7617922572975577}
{"id": "nat_127", "text": "The long drought burned the crops dry.", "audio_duration_s": 2.414875283446712, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.429881633377863, "dnsmos_sig": 3.6530178453857127, "dnsmos_bak": 4.1732792238491445}
{"id": "nat_128", "text": "The cool air smelled of pine and earth.", "audio_duration_s": 2.461315192743764, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.0746648973869077, "dnsmos_sig": 3.546989848406113, "dnsmos_bak": 3.726291278368204}
{"id": "nat_129", "text": "The child ran barefoot in the wet grass.", "audio_duration_s": 2.36843537414966, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.362558375138741, "dnsmos_sig": 3.6093448740181286, "dnsmos_bak": 4.104143384033196}
{"id": "nat_130", "text": "A kite soared high above the park.", "audio_duration_s": 2.182675736961451, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.3251828340650795, "dnsmos_sig": 3.6028209103119235, "dnsmos_bak": 4.057959170458515}
{"id": "nat_131", "text": "The bridge shook as the truck rolled past.", "audio_duration_s": 2.461315192743764, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.445078875358133, "dnsmos_sig": 3.667033599265978, "dnsmos_bak": 4.123786236520728}
{"id": "nat_132", "text": "The soft light fell on the open book.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9504761904761905, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.070407552195475, "dnsmos_sig": 3.4068645762053626, "dnsmos_bak": 3.8705420832748936}
{"id": "nat_133", "text": "The crane lifted the heavy steel beam.", "audio_duration_s": 2.2291156462585033, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.238885696688438, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5534212604072613, "dnsmos_bak": 4.027209170657284}
{"id": "nat_134", "text": "The strong horse pulled the loaded cart.", "audio_duration_s": 2.36843537414966, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.219678789298949, "dnsmos_sig": 3.4819528787223946, "dnsmos_bak": 4.031780932670124}
{"id": "nat_135", "text": "The wind died down as night came on.", "audio_duration_s": 2.414875283446712, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.1551813281150114, "dnsmos_sig": 3.4976812986246553, "dnsmos_bak": 3.9438054720860443}
{"id": "nat_136", "text": "The bird built its nest in the fork of the branch.", "audio_duration_s": 2.507755102040816, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.3129159743449192, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5812378488105168, "dnsmos_bak": 4.102985817022141}
{"id": "nat_137", "text": "The ice was thin near the river bank.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9504761904761905, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.207226248567924, "dnsmos_sig": 3.4540330760387534, "dnsmos_bak": 4.069693292808705}
{"id": "nat_138", "text": "The fog lifted slowly as the sun rose.", "audio_duration_s": 2.693514739229025, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 2.940407957292091, "dnsmos_sig": 3.3299677629947366, "dnsmos_bak": 3.7720316991471936}
{"id": "nat_139", "text": "The fire crackled in the stone hearth.", "audio_duration_s": 2.136235827664399, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.399302440441043, "dnsmos_sig": 3.6324381435184767, "dnsmos_bak": 4.099829956937358}
{"id": "nat_140", "text": "The long bridge arched over the bay.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9504761904761905, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.1248689645297376, "dnsmos_sig": 3.3802120383959653, "dnsmos_bak": 4.059373059783387}
{"id": "nat_141", "text": "A cloud of dust rose from the dry road.", "audio_duration_s": 2.36843537414966, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.3120240964813203, "dnsmos_sig": 3.6119171689377496, "dnsmos_bak": 4.076766113971947}
{"id": "nat_142", "text": "The swift stream ran over smooth stones.", "audio_duration_s": 2.693514739229025, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2590377871547314, "dnsmos_sig": 3.509098933568288, "dnsmos_bak": 4.042781567711642}
{"id": "nat_143", "text": "The torch cast shadows on the old wall.", "audio_duration_s": 2.36843537414966, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.065158264735688, "dnsmos_sig": 3.529774547851372, "dnsmos_bak": 3.812944079963546}
{"id": "nat_144", "text": "The net was full of silver fish.", "audio_duration_s": 2.182675736961451, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.247993051558118, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5398604553060014, "dnsmos_bak": 4.059813798371953}
{"id": "nat_145", "text": "The tall grain stood ripe in the field.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9504761904761905, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 2.8347571591585545, "dnsmos_sig": 3.319237237103612, "dnsmos_bak": 3.6678342442559893}
{"id": "nat_146", "text": "The damp cloth wiped the dusty shelf.", "audio_duration_s": 2.2755555555555556, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.3671533662049287, "dnsmos_sig": 3.628750949758838, "dnsmos_bak": 4.173844987196834}
{"id": "nat_147", "text": "A mule team pulled the heavy plow.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9504761904761905, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.4443840634009057, "dnsmos_sig": 3.6565510708951865, "dnsmos_bak": 4.181471351244753}
{"id": "nat_148", "text": "The old chair sat in the corner unused.", "audio_duration_s": 2.507755102040816, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.1797434520863117, "dnsmos_sig": 3.4494454173524147, "dnsmos_bak": 4.015648794227024}
{"id": "nat_149", "text": "The rain fell steadily through the night.", "audio_duration_s": 2.089795918367347, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.0790628348777136, "dnsmos_sig": 3.3853110152025363, "dnsmos_bak": 3.9603578417278014}
{"id": "nat_150", "text": "The lantern hung from the low beam.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9040362811791383, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 2.5234298721979744, "dnsmos_sig": 3.3014590859691904, "dnsmos_bak": 3.058357370348464}
{"id": "nat_151", "text": "The wind brought the smell of fresh hay.", "audio_duration_s": 2.3219954648526078, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.1082314922974206, "dnsmos_sig": 3.421163851131584, "dnsmos_bak": 3.9633653034613268}
{"id": "nat_152", "text": "The stone path led to the small gate.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9969160997732427, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 2.7913758327819296, "dnsmos_sig": 3.278663546593684, "dnsmos_bak": 3.5568647606131862}
{"id": "nat_153", "text": "The loud noise startled the sleeping dog.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9969160997732427, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.042761957879835, "dnsmos_sig": 3.4734496975967306, "dnsmos_bak": 3.714420327306094}
{"id": "nat_154", "text": "The canoe glided across the glassy lake.", "audio_duration_s": 2.2291156462585033, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2453249359381866, "dnsmos_sig": 3.574518495097009, "dnsmos_bak": 4.016698858862412}
{"id": "nat_155", "text": "The long journey left them very tired.", "audio_duration_s": 2.089795918367347, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.229042733891053, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5016252959302383, "dnsmos_bak": 4.094169282267986}
{"id": "nat_156", "text": "The lark sang early in the damp morning.", "audio_duration_s": 2.089795918367347, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.25060884745577, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5314987171819907, "dnsmos_bak": 4.0840179945484305}
{"id": "nat_157", "text": "The bees hummed in the tall clover.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9504761904761905, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.193284172635412, "dnsmos_sig": 3.477288492580202, "dnsmos_bak": 4.032849187966144}
{"id": "nat_158", "text": "The thick ice covered the frozen pond.", "audio_duration_s": 2.182675736961451, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.016521896598512, "dnsmos_sig": 3.536594161909524, "dnsmos_bak": 3.671559590454314}
{"id": "nat_159", "text": "The young deer grazed near the tree line.", "audio_duration_s": 2.2291156462585033, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.141877857181842, "dnsmos_sig": 3.4886954921516526, "dnsmos_bak": 3.9004070019322628}
{"id": "nat_160", "text": "The heavy rains swelled the quiet river.", "audio_duration_s": 2.043356009070295, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.225603643740467, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5286072841280354, "dnsmos_bak": 4.015808045518379}
{"id": "nat_161", "text": "The steep cliff dropped to the blue sea.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9504761904761905, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 2.686172309467532, "dnsmos_sig": 3.009977812028398, "dnsmos_bak": 3.825456942996464}
{"id": "nat_162", "text": "The bright sparks flew from the anvil.", "audio_duration_s": 2.089795918367347, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2070483360260904, "dnsmos_sig": 3.490359438787067, "dnsmos_bak": 3.9967690478256337}
{"id": "nat_163", "text": "The cold spring fed the old stone trough.", "audio_duration_s": 2.972154195011338, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.350297866140767, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5976242384206136, "dnsmos_bak": 4.1051956609125115}
{"id": "nat_164", "text": "The wild geese flew south at dusk.", "audio_duration_s": 2.136235827664399, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.115927190251731, "dnsmos_sig": 3.4389829360063113, "dnsmos_bak": 3.942850023308658}
{"id": "nat_165", "text": "The soft moss covered the old log.", "audio_duration_s": 2.043356009070295, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.3982417478978126, "dnsmos_sig": 3.6364621349234567, "dnsmos_bak": 4.137638634323772}
{"id": "nat_166", "text": "The sun shone warm on the stone bench.", "audio_duration_s": 2.507755102040816, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.1825223578042316, "dnsmos_sig": 3.4840591170831816, "dnsmos_bak": 3.9736690377695965}
{"id": "nat_167", "text": "The fresh bread smelled good in the kitchen.", "audio_duration_s": 2.182675736961451, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2723879886633678, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5383068664020567, "dnsmos_bak": 4.065722931755095}
{"id": "nat_168", "text": "The frog leaped from the muddy bank.", "audio_duration_s": 1.811156462585034, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 2.9835543843051253, "dnsmos_sig": 3.322537857514013, "dnsmos_bak": 3.866121035029285}
{"id": "nat_169", "text": "The tall ship sailed out of the harbor.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9040362811791383, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.154427875865323, "dnsmos_sig": 3.4409503391846386, "dnsmos_bak": 3.9904106619997113}
{"id": "nat_170", "text": "The thick smoke rose from the chimney.", "audio_duration_s": 2.089795918367347, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.1714754365537274, "dnsmos_sig": 3.523807372806449, "dnsmos_bak": 3.8872973024678026}
{"id": "nat_171", "text": "The black cat sat on the warm sill.", "audio_duration_s": 2.182675736961451, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.126936622836805, "dnsmos_sig": 3.499492475920816, "dnsmos_bak": 3.831825933524108}
{"id": "nat_172", "text": "The wide valley lay green and still.", "audio_duration_s": 2.043356009070295, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.214694218821929, "dnsmos_sig": 3.4942960865812998, "dnsmos_bak": 4.088997105093873}
{"id": "nat_173", "text": "The old well ran dry in late summer.", "audio_duration_s": 2.414875283446712, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2167514447786596, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5023149655223844, "dnsmos_bak": 4.087857192467627}
{"id": "nat_174", "text": "The cold snap froze the small brook.", "audio_duration_s": 2.2291156462585033, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 2.892905500048286, "dnsmos_sig": 3.4819557727584303, "dnsmos_bak": 3.424415840817327}
{"id": "nat_175", "text": "The dew dried quickly in the warm sun.", "audio_duration_s": 2.136235827664399, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.3135445063911155, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5873754579731916, "dnsmos_bak": 4.078029943676492}
{"id": "nat_176", "text": "The sharp smell of pine filled the air.", "audio_duration_s": 2.089795918367347, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.1799225098701394, "dnsmos_sig": 3.4579488221532304, "dnsmos_bak": 4.0530713061590316}
{"id": "nat_177", "text": "The dog barked once and then was still.", "audio_duration_s": 2.182675736961451, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 2.9898660517118096, "dnsmos_sig": 3.35206645132263, "dnsmos_bak": 3.84553796883383}
{"id": "nat_178", "text": "The clay jar cracked in the dry heat.", "audio_duration_s": 2.089795918367347, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.1583916436282173, "dnsmos_sig": 3.484132513335445, "dnsmos_bak": 4.02216088588372}
{"id": "nat_179", "text": "The loom wove cloth of many colors.", "audio_duration_s": 2.182675736961451, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2257968365495695, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5217545557716625, "dnsmos_bak": 3.9800403874748924}
{"id": "nat_180", "text": "The brook flowed cold and clear all year.", "audio_duration_s": 2.647074829931973, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.0029532061330895, "dnsmos_sig": 3.4459193661376664, "dnsmos_bak": 3.675416652090272}
{"id": "nat_181", "text": "The frost burned the last of the corn.", "audio_duration_s": 2.2291156462585033, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.272438373493396, "dnsmos_sig": 3.6029548435066787, "dnsmos_bak": 4.028651005311214}
{"id": "nat_182", "text": "The long canoe was carved from a log.", "audio_duration_s": 2.182675736961451, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.205460407323386, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5680924170562807, "dnsmos_bak": 3.96443852395955}
{"id": "nat_183", "text": "The roan horse ran best on flat ground.", "audio_duration_s": 2.414875283446712, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2713960718118145, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5763188059172983, "dnsmos_bak": 4.060553972361292}
{"id": "nat_184", "text": "The fern grew thick in the dark hollow.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9969160997732427, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.178370730556662, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5068237545445373, "dnsmos_bak": 3.9327600194494163}
{"id": "nat_185", "text": "The sharp taste of the brine filled his mouth.", "audio_duration_s": 2.36843537414966, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.1207093966765496, "dnsmos_sig": 3.399739969925847, "dnsmos_bak": 3.986970140540537}
{"id": "nat_186", "text": "The cart horse stood still in the rain.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9504761904761905, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 2.9482635875365073, "dnsmos_sig": 3.314916162789133, "dnsmos_bak": 3.743803324136408}
{"id": "nat_187", "text": "The red brick house faced the park.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9969160997732427, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.0475685779643595, "dnsmos_sig": 3.375867061557617, "dnsmos_bak": 3.905397093065545}
{"id": "nat_188", "text": "The pale dawn light filled the valley.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9504761904761905, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.207960806133411, "dnsmos_sig": 3.498953512179123, "dnsmos_bak": 4.056108924702013}
{"id": "nat_189", "text": "The dry wood burned hot and fast.", "audio_duration_s": 2.2755555555555556, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.0569593685113916, "dnsmos_sig": 3.387878074624422, "dnsmos_bak": 3.888618180547402}
{"id": "nat_190", "text": "The neural network achieved state-of-the-art performance on the benchmark.", "audio_duration_s": 3.6687528344671203, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.3667256457604644, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5983687342555832, "dnsmos_bak": 4.143256381028818}
{"id": "nat_191", "text": "Please confirm your appointment for tomorrow at three o'clock.", "audio_duration_s": 2.9257142857142857, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.438578822858865, "dnsmos_sig": 3.693288040471132, "dnsmos_bak": 4.14418072936126}
{"id": "nat_192", "text": "The quarterly earnings report exceeded analyst expectations by twelve percent.", "audio_duration_s": 4.4117913832199545, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.3285099514179786, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5970433787950844, "dnsmos_bak": 4.107436112859357}
{"id": "nat_193", "text": "We regret to inform you that your flight has been delayed by two hours.", "audio_duration_s": 3.6687528344671203, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2069990603885747, "dnsmos_sig": 3.4464185371353073, "dnsmos_bak": 4.116905207109416}
{"id": "nat_194", "text": "The temperature today will reach a high of seventy-two degrees Fahrenheit.", "audio_duration_s": 3.622312925170068, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.1538213700318676, "dnsmos_sig": 3.4605099996851605, "dnsmos_bak": 3.9670242207857123}
{"id": "nat_195", "text": "Your order has been shipped and will arrive within three to five business days.", "audio_duration_s": 3.8080725623582765, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.328518859894434, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5571381295662445, "dnsmos_bak": 4.139894450768719}
{"id": "nat_196", "text": "The new software update includes several important security patches.", "audio_duration_s": 3.575873015873016, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.3842778199262717, "dnsmos_sig": 3.6048042842054087, "dnsmos_bak": 4.1583336710884025}
{"id": "nat_197", "text": "Press one for English, press two for Spanish, or stay on the line.", "audio_duration_s": 3.7616326530612243, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.1981552819223236, "dnsmos_sig": 3.478994361097458, "dnsmos_bak": 4.0122527441315095}
{"id": "nat_198", "text": "The meeting has been rescheduled to next Tuesday at two thirty PM.", "audio_duration_s": 3.8080725623582765, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2142000211882813, "dnsmos_sig": 3.4478262219537807, "dnsmos_bak": 4.129175107984318}
{"id": "nat_199", "text": "Thank you for calling customer support. How can I assist you today?", "audio_duration_s": 3.7151927437641725, "utmos": null, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.3786208714822066, "dnsmos_sig": 3.591088108645375, "dnsmos_bak": 4.160130823370414}
